Class Team<T extends Individual>

  • java.lang.Object
    • MAE1Project.Team<T>
  • public class Team<T extends Individual>
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Felix Zapata Date: 3/04/2019 Team is a Java Generics class which can only accept as type variable any child from Individual. Thus, it constitutes a Java Generics with bounded type variable. The idea behind this class is to reduce the amount of code required.
